  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t国人反美/反西方，并不是反霸权，也未必是反自由民主。其实，他们主要反的、恐惧的，是图中这些，是为了避免在性侵害女性、伤害儿童、欺凌弱势群体、施行体制暴力……之后被绳之以法，或者起码不能再随心所欲的性侵害、虐待、欺凌、屠杀，以及其他在黑箱中和暗处做下的行为。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n为了避免这样的下场，或者起码不能为所欲为、保有既得利益，所以他们需要拼命反西方、保卫只有邪恶体制才能得到且不受惩罚（甚至鼓励，仅仅选择性惩罚不听话者）的一切<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTI5YWE0YmRjY2M0ZmNlYmQ4MTNlLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a29aa4bdccc4fcebd813e.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a29aa4bdccc4fcebd813e.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a29aa4bdccc4fcebd813e.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZWZhOTY4OWM0NGQ5ZWFiNzYyYTM5LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/efa9689c44d9eab762a39.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/efa9689c44d9eab762a39.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/efa9689c44d9eab762a39.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMWI1YjdlOTRjNjVmZTA3Mjk5Y2Q0LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1b5b7e94c65fe07299cd4.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1b5b7e94c65fe07299cd4.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1b5b7e94c65fe07299cd4.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZWU2NzE2YjdiNjI5ZjdmMDQzZGY2LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ee6716b7b629f7f043df6.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ee6716b7b629f7f043df6.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ee6716b7b629f7f043df6.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMGZmMTZiMGVkZGE1MzU3MjZmZjdjLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow n